name: LAX VR
summary: LAX VR is the ultimate first-person VR lacrosse experience, featuring both Box and Field play—including an exhilarating 6v6 field game where you can step in as a field player, long pole, or goalie. Game modes include Field, Box, Braveheart, Shooting, Goalie, Longstick, Shoot Around, and Wall Ball. The Medicine Game honors the Indigenous origins of lacrosse in a mythical historic setting. Hone your skills, customize your twig, and chase a championship in Box or Field 6v6 tournaments.
